      <head>Max Adler</head>
      <div>

        <p> Viennese sociologist and socialist theoretician, also professor at Vienna University. </p>
          
          <p>Like Otto Bauer, he was one of the theoreticians of Austro-Marxism. In his school of
          Neo-Kantianism, he attempted to combine the teaching of Karl Marx with the ideas of Kant,
          proposing a socialist model of life and culture, within which he coined the term "The New
          Man" ("homo futura" or "der neue Mensch").</p>
      </div>
